@entity markdown
  @added 2.0.0
  @description
    A renderer for rendering @code[markdown] using quantum

    Example Code:
    @@codeblock markdown
      @@markdown
        # Example heading

        Example _italic_ or **bold** text.


    Example Result:
    @@markdown
      # Example heading
      Example _italic_ or **bold** text.


    @code(um)[@inline] can also be used:
    @@codeblock um
      @markdown: @inline path/to/file.md
